{"service_name": "INFOSEC Supply Chain Assurance", "service_id": "7682990133271321", "company_name": "Selex ES Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Selex ES Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     INFOSEC Supply Chain Assurance\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Audit services specifically designed for the HMG supply chain. CLAS staff provide audit services attuned to the scope of supply, to measure and improve the security supporting the services or products being provided. Reporting of audits is specific to client requirements and appropriate to the security classification and product/service risk.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Audit services specifically for the HMG supply chain\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Measure and improve security supporting services or products being provided\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Practices adapted to fit project operational and cultural requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Datum will be selected in discussion with client\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Blends the prevailing contract, ISO28002:2011, ISO27001:2013 and SPF information\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Consultants are CLAS accredited and Lead Auditor trained for ISO27001:2013\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Fully aligned with requirements of ISO27001:2013\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Experience from related sectors such as local Government and Defence\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Balances excellent customer service with efficient and secure operations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ISO27001 used to assess supply chains\u2019 resilience to security incidents\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Reduces risk through effective management of supply chain security\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Insurance of compliance with Customer and Industry standards.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supply chains assessed for resilience to security incident disruption\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Considers on shore and off shore risks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance checks including   Data Protection, Computer Misuse et al\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assurance that suppliers are looking after sensitive assets\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Documented output with observations to facilitate issue tracking\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3609 to \u00a31386 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92392/7682990133271321-pricing-document-2015-10-01-0733.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92392/7682990133271321-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-01-0733.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n   